    "description": "Valve has removed the game 'Fursan al-Aqsa: The Knights of the Al-Aqsa Mosque' from its UK Steam storefront after a request from the UK's Counter Terrorism Internet Referral Unit. The game, which was updated to reference a recent Hamas attack, has also been banned in Germany and Australia.",
